# Environment Variables for Public App

## Required Variables

# Supabase Configuration
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=http://localhost:54321
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_anon_key_here

# Hub App Integration (for "Tambah Iklan" redirect)
NEXT_PUBLIC_HUB_URL=http://localhost:3000

# TV Display Integration (for "Lihat Paparan" links)
NEXT_PUBLIC_TV_DISPLAY_URL=http://localhost:3001/display

## Optional Variables

# Google Analytics (leave empty for development)
NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_ID=

# App Configuration
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_NAME=masjidbro.my
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_DESCRIPTION=Platform paparan iklan masjid seluruh Malaysia

## Notes
# - NEXT_PUBLIC_ prefix makes variables available in browser
# - Never commit .env.local with real API keys
# - For production, set these in Vercel/hosting platform environment
